#!/usr/bin/tail -n+2

                                 [44;1m How it works [0m



               PShT is a shell library that provides a simple and

              standardized way to step through slides. Any program

                or script can serve as a slide, as long as it's

                         in the `_slides` subdirectory.



          The _slides folder in the source repository can serve as an

                                    example.
